racter in  Charlotte Brontë's  novel Jane Eyre (  1847 ). From  1932 to 1959  it was used as the name of a cheerful and scantily clad beauty whose adventures were chronicled in a strip cartoon in the Daily Mirror. It is also borne by the American film stars  Jane Russell  (  1921–2011 ) and  Jane Fonda  (  b. 1937 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sire d'Aulnay was born about 1260, in France. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"estimated 1260–":"umbes 1260–Surnud","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1260–Male":"1260–Surnud","estimated 1260":"umbes 1260","1275":"1275","1260":"1260","1319":"1319","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"estimated 1260–":"noin 1260–Kuollut","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1260–Male":"1260–Kuollut","estimated 1260":"noin 1260","1275":"1275","1260":"1260","1319":"1319","France":"Ranska"},"fr":{"estimated 1260–":"environ 1260–Décédé","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1260–Male":"1260–Décédé","estimated 1260":"environ 1260","1275":"1275","1260":"1260","1319":"1319","France":"France","lifeSummary":"Sire d'Aulnay est né environ 1260, à France. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"estimated 1260–":"um 1260–Verstorben","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1260–Male":"1260–Verstorben","estimated 1260":"um 1260","1275":"1275","1260":"1260","1319":"1319","France":"Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Sire d'Aulnay wurde um 1260 in Frankreich geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"estimated 1260–":"about 1260–Desede","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1260–Male":"1260–Desede","estimated 1260":"about 1260","1275":"1275","1260":"1260","1319":"1319","France":"France"},"hu":{"estimated 1260–":"1260 körül–elhunyt","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1260–Male":"1260–elhunyt","estimated 1260":"1260 körül","1275":"1275","1260":"1260","1319":"1319","France":"Franciaország"},"id":{"estimated 1260–":"sekitar 1260–Telah Meninggal","1275–1319":"1275–1319","1260–Male":"1260–Telah Meninggal","estimated 1260":"sekitar 1260","1275":"1275","1260":"1260","1319":"1319","France":"Prancis"},"it":{"estimated 1260–":"circa 1260–Deceduto","1275–1319":"1275–13